    <p>The SAVE (Saving on a Valuable Education) plan replaced the REPAYE plan in 2023 and is generally the most generous income-driven option for most borrowers. It offers the lowest payment percentage for undergraduate loans, a higher income protection threshold, and a provision that prevents your balance from growing due to unpaid interest as long as you make your scheduled payments.</p>

